{"tid":43770,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"真心覺得韓國冷面幾好食","createTime":"2016-12-17T17:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T01:50:50.000Z","uid":42097,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67b20dae70709fbc5e6a0d92c81d4f46c658f8a2","tid":43770,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"日式個種鰹魚冷麵味道太重<br />\n有候食幾啖就唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對比韓式冷面個冷湯一般比較淡<br />\n同時啲麵幼好多，口感上絕對比日式冷麵優勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然高登仔屌韓式料理屌得多，我都係其中一份子<br />\n食過試過會發現，其實韓式料理簡便中都有一啲精品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道一定會有人屌我support 韓國野<br />\n但係依次真係食過覺得好食先開po 鳩up下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f28573eb12e780c4cf12391767bb76c1dd6796","tid":43770,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"杏色冷湯一般都係蘋果醋/酸白蘿蔔<br />\n味道帶酸而且甜甜地<br />\n食完真係會覺得幾涼爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/011538_cec2d689ac4d6a9cd3e770025e6faf99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F011538_cec2d689ac4d6a9cd3e770025e6faf99.jpg&h=d9e1ab98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b304d37e408ff115879f02c9677f9f93378360d","tid":43770,"uid":49977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T01:48:45.000Z","msg":"水冷麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d麵質又彈牙啲"},{"pid":"82c8ad16f8d4c38e765591e36a058c8cb045be9a","tid":43770,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"平壤冷麵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}